description: Creates an import job for an address list.

parameters.name: AddressListId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the address list for importing addresses to.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: A unique token that Amazon SES uses to recognize subsequent retries of the same request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: ImportDataFormat
parameters.description: The format of the input for an import job. The type of file that would be passed as an input for the address list import job.

nested_params.name: ImportDataType
nested_params.description: The type of file that would be passed as an input for the address list import job.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: A user-friendly name for the import job.

nested_items.name: JobId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the created import job.

nested_items.name: PreSignedUrl
nested_items.description: The pre-signed URL target for uploading the input file.
